{"segment":5,"line_start":396,"line_end":494,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","speaker_name":"司马超群","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"我知道，早已知道，做丈夫的并不一定是最后知道的一个。","tone":"平静","chapter":15,"line_start":424,"line_end":424},{"speaker":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","speaker_name":"司马超群","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"我也知道那件事很快就会过去的，她还是会做我的好妻子，还是会好好照顾我的孩子。","tone":"平静","chapter":15,"line_start":426,"line_end":426},{"speaker":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","speaker_name":"司马超群","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"我既然决心要依照你的意思做一个了不起的大英雄，就必需付出代价。","tone":"淡然","chapter":15,"line_start":432,"line_end":432},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","text":"所以你就故意装做不知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":436,"line_end":436},{"speaker":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","speaker_name":"司马超群","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"那一点点屈辱，一点点痛苦，我总还忍受得了。","tone":"痛苦","chapter":15,"line_start":442,"line_end":442},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","text":"我看错你了。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":15,"line_start":446,"line_end":446},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","text":"所以你就认为你已经尽到做丈夫的责任了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":452,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","speaker_name":"司马超群","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"不。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":456,"line_end":456},{"speaker":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","speaker_name":"司马超群","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"可是我却没有尽到做丈夫的责任，所以错的是我，不是她。","tone":"悲痛","chapter":15,"line_start":460,"line_end":460},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","text":"她错了。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":466,"line_end":466},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_si_ma_chao_qun","text":"我知道这些话并不是你真心要说出来的。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":15,"line_start":470,"line_end":470},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speake